    {
      "id": "10",
      "name": "Description",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "story",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p>This was a story from long ago...</p><p><br>Unborn life, unfulfilled wishes,<br>Tragic dreams at the edge of the universal darkness that could never come true,<br>Indwell my body, and descend unto this world.</p><p><br>Then, my lovely children,<br>Like rainwater flowing into creeks, and plants growing towards the sun,<br>Go unto a lovely place, and display your own beauty there with pride.</p><p><br>This is a memory, a memory that a child named Durin had of his mother...</p><p><br>&#34;Thank you, Mother, thank you.&#34;<br>&#34;You gave me wings to soar and a mighty form.&#34;<br>&#34;Mother, I wish to go to a land of lovely songs,&#34;<br>&#34;I will tell them about you, Mother, and about everyone else.&#34;<br>&#34;I shall tell them that the place where I was born is beautiful.&#34;</p>",
                "title": ""
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
